channel.title: 50-70 Ranged
channel.description: Every guide I've looked at don't have effective ways of training ranged, so I'm asking what you guys think the most effective and relatively cheap way of training range (including equipment and monsters) from level 50-70.

item.title: 50-70 Ranged
item.dc:creator: @Incognito Incognito
item.description:
@Incognito wrote:

Wow, too many bots on RuneScape nowadays, huh? If you ain’t gonna train, don’t play. That’s my opinion.

But anyways… I trained my range, back when I was a member, at the experiments. They don’t damage you, and they have 1,000 HP. Always kill the level 25 ones though, the higher ones have less HP. But when I trained there I could raise it fairly quick. I also only used iron arrows and raped them quick. I think you get around 540 exp. total per experiment.
But yeah, that was my cheap way of training as a member. Killing those.

Best of luck!
-Incognito

item.title: 50-70 Ranged
item.dc:creator: @Echo3 Echo_
item.description:
@Echo3 wrote:

Knives/darts at rock crabs or yaks, you can also use a cannon while your doing it for extra xp per hour. That’ s that fastest way I have found to get 70 range, and I have done it on a few accounts. If you think your losing too much money with the cannon, you could use it at Dragons, Ankous, or even Black Demons for crimsons instead.

item.title: 50-70 Ranged
item.dc:creator: @Spades Spades
item.description:
@Spades wrote:

[quote=“the elve age, post:16, topic:377802”][quote author=Jc22493 link=topic=473688.msg3464289#msg3464289 date=1294779649]
I would just cannon it.
[/quote]

That would take ages. And cost like 20mil.[/quote]

It wouldn’t take a long time, and it sure wouldn’t cost 20M. You can easily find a dead world and set it up at dragons and make back cash and a half EASILY. Dragon bones being like 4.5k and hides being like 3k. You would use ~5-10 cannon balls per dragon plus you attacking them aswell, you will make 1-2k per kill getting ~500 kills per hour. you will find yourself making 300-400k easily per hour. Without the cannon you can make 1M per hour at dragons if you kill them fast enough.

item.title: 50-70 Ranged
item.dc:creator: @rip4d rip4d
item.description:
@rip4d wrote:

Tzhaar. If you’re able to, get some broad bolts and an adamant crossbow and kill tzhaar monsters. If not that, a magic shortbow and a shitton of iron or steel arrows. At 61, move on to a rune crossbow, and wear void ranged armor if you can. TzHaar isn’t the fastest xp, but you can generally chat with people nearby and its fun getting obsidian drops (even though they aren’t worth nearly as much anymore… I hope they return to 300k for a shield and such <.<)

Oh yea, pick up Tokkul, ALWAYS. Its worth 6.8 each if going for an onyx, and ~3 each for shields last time I checked.
